===Cardinal number===
'''trillion'''
# (''US; modern British & Australian'') A [[million]] million; a 1 followed by twelve zeros; 10<sup>12</sup>.
# (''Dated usage, British & Australian'') A million million million; 1 followed by eighteen zeros; 10<sup>18</sup>.

*''Western (Arabic) Numeral'' '''Trillion, 10<sup>12</sup>'''
